;SDL

;===================================
;        INSTRUCTIONS    
;===================================

; In this file onee configures the humans which are spawned in vehicles or squads
; The humans have a CP and cost associated with them which collectively add up for the final squad value
; Check ../settings_inf.set for the global defines for CP, capture weight (CW), score, etc.

;===================================
;        PRICING CHART	       
;===================================

; // Standard prices below are for tier2 infantry

;pistol 		= 5
;p14 			= 8
;enfield no1 	= 9
;enfield no4 	= 9
;sten	 		= 10
;patchett	 	= 10
;thompson 20	= 9
;thompson 30	= 10
;bren			= 25
;lewis			= 35
;vgo			= 40
;rifle grenade 	= +10 or 5 if squad
;piat 			= +60
;mortar 		= +50
;any % pzfaust 	= +0
;any pzfaust 	= +0
;any flamer		= 55
;engineer		= 50 or 25 if squad
;miner 			= 40 or 25 if squad

; // price modifiers (If not tier2)
;tier 0 		= -3, MG -10
;tier 1 		= -1, MG -10
;tier 1 vet 	= 0, MG 0
;tier 2 vet		= +2, MG +5
;tier 3 		= +5, MG +10
;tier 3 vet 	= +8, MG +15
;tier 4 		= +10, MG +20
;tier 4 vet 	= +12, MG +25


